(17, 'OnePlus 11R Review', '<p><strong>OnePlus 11R %G </strong>OnePlus is before long going to deliver a few cell phones in the Indian cell phone market and the gadgets are intended to cook the mid-range segment. There are different bits of hearsay that OnePlus is chipping away at the OnePlus 11R Smartphone and the gadget will stir things up around town as well as Indian market soon with a 120Hz revive rate screen, a Qualcomm Snapdragon chipset, enough Slam and capacity alongside 5G network. We should investigate the OnePlus 11R cost in India and different specs that have proactively surfaced on the web.This phone has a number of features that make it stand out from the competition, including a beautiful design and top-notch performance. In this blog post, we&acirc;&euro;&trade;ll take a closer look at this impressive phone and discuss some of its key benefits.</p>\r\n<p> OnePlus is all set to launch their latest smartphone, the OnePlus 11R. We&acirc;&euro;&trade;ll also provide tips on how to get the most out of it and maximize its potential. So be sure to check this out if you&acirc;&euro;&trade;re considering purchasing a new phone!<br />\r\nIf you&acirc;&euro;&trade;re one of the many OnePlus fans eagerly awaiting the release of the OnePlus 11R, you&acirc;&euro;&trade;ll be happy to know that it&acirc;&euro;&trade;s finally available to buy in India. In this blog post, we&acirc;&euro;&trade;ll take a look at the OnePlus 11R and its features, as well as provide an overview of the price and release date in India. So whether you&acirc;&euro;&trade;re looking to upgrade your current phone or purchase your first Android flagship, be sure to check out this blog post for all the latest information. The OnePlus 11R cost in India is supposed to be Rs. 45,490. </p><p>OnePlus 11R comes with 8 GB Slam/128 GB inner capacity base variation of OnePlus 11R as would be considered normal to accessible in Dark, Gold tone.OnePlus has always been a company that focuses on delivering the best possible experience to its users. And the OnePlus 11R is no exception. This new phone not only offers great performance, but it&acirc;&euro;&trade;s also stylish and affordable. great mobile with features at an affordable price, then the OnePlus 11R is a great option. This mobile offers a range of great features, including a fascinating new camera system that promises better photos and videos. Additionally, it comes with a number of other great features, including an updated processor and improved battery life. In this article, we&acirc;&euro;&trade;ll take a look at the OnePlus 11R price in India in 2023. So whether you&acirc;&euro;&trade;re in the market for a new phone or just want to know what the latest prices are, read on!</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>OnePlus 11R 5G : Specs</h3>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p><strong>OnePlus 11R 5G specs</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Screen:</td>\r\n			<td>6.55 inches (16.63 cm)</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Resolution:</td>\r\n			<td>1080 x 2400 Pixels</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>CPU:</td>\r\n			<td>Qualcomm</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>RAM:</td>\r\n			<td>8 GB</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Storage:</td>\r\n			<td>128GB</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>OS:</td>\r\n			<td>Android v11</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Rear Cameras:</td>\r\n			<td>50 MP + 13 MP + 2 MP</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Front Camera:</td>\r\n			<td>16 MP</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Battery:</td>\r\n			<td>5,000mAh</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<h3>OnePlus 11R Features</h3>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>OnePlus 11R is a lead venture outfitted with a plenty of cutting edge highlights. Its multi-layered design sheet is good to go to give a satisfying functional encounter all through. Likewise, a 128GB inner space and Android v12 operating system stacked inside are of extraordinary assistance.OnePlus 11R will be available for purchase on Amazon India from February 21st. The phone will come with 6GB of RAM and 128GB of internal storage. It will also have a triple rear camera setup with a telephoto lens, a standard lens and a ultra-wide lens. It will run on the Android 9 Pie operating system.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>&nbsp;Pros</h3>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Great performance</li>\r\n	<li>Premium design</li>\r\n	<li>Decent primary camera</li>\r\n	<li>Good battery life</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h3>&nbsp;Cons</h3>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Ultra-wide and macro sensors can be improved</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h3>OnePlus 11R Reviews</h3>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>If you&acirc;&euro;&trade;re in the market for a new phone, the OnePlus 11R should definitely be on your list. This phone has some great features that will make your life easier, and it&acirc;&euro;&trade;s backed by a great warranty. Plus, it comes at a great price point. In this blog post, we&acirc;&euro;&trade;ll take a look at some of the best features of the OnePlus 11R, and we&acirc;&euro;&trade;ll also give you our verdict on whether or not it&acirc;&euro;&trade;s worth buying. So read on to find out all you need to know about this phone!If you&acirc;&euro;&trade;re in the market for a new mobile phone, you&acirc;&euro;&trade;re in for a real treat. Not only does the OnePlus 11R offer top-of-the-line performance, but it&acirc;&euro;&trade;s also one of the most affordable phones on the market. In this blog post, we will discuss the OnePlus 11R in detail and provide an overview of its impressive features. We will also discuss its price in India in 2023, so that you can be sure you&acirc;&euro;&trade;re getting your money&acirc;&euro;&trade;s worth.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Conclusion</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>If you&acirc;&euro;&trade;re looking for a phone that&acirc;&euro;&trade;s going to give you excellent performance in a variety of scenarios, the OnePlus 11R is a great option. It has a Snapdragon 855 SoC, which is going to offer you excellent performance when it comes to gaming and other intensive tasks. It also has a lot of the features that you would expect from a flagship phone, such as an advanced camera system and an immersive display. Overall, the OnePlus 11R is a great phone that offers excellent value for money.</p>\r\n', './blog_images/oneplus.jpg', 1, 4, '2024-01-29 16:58:25'),
(19, 'Redmi Note 12 Pro 5G | Review', '<p>Xiaomi Redmi Note 12 Pro &acirc;&euro;&ldquo; Subsequent to sending off the Redmi Note 12 5G series in China, Xiaomi has affirmed that it will send off a new cell phone under a similar series in the country. The forthcoming Redmi Note 12 Expert Speed Release will send off close by the Redmi K60 series on December 27th in China. Xiaomi has affirmed the Qualcomm Snapdragon 778G 5G chipset is said to drive the telephone. It is one of the most remarkable midrange chipsets available.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The Xiaomi Redmi Note 12 Pro 5G cost in India is supposed to be Rs. 20,590. Xiaomi Redmi Note 12 Ace 5G Expected to be sent off on Jan 05, 2023. This is 6 GB Smash/128 GB inward capacity base variation of Xiaomi Redmi Note 12 Star 5G as would be considered normal to accessible in Dark, Blue, White, Violet tone.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Mi Redmi Note 12 Pro was launched in August last year. Xiaomi has been a pioneer in the low-cost smartphone segment and has always been aggressive in pushing the envelope with its hardware and software. The Redmi Note 12 Pro is an impressive handset that offers a lot of features at an affordable price. In this article, we will be taking a look at the price of Xiaomi Redmi Note 12 Pro in India 2023.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>As far as show, the organization has uncovered that the impending cell phone will include an OLED show, and the screen of the cell phone will stay level. It very well may be normal that there will be a poke hole pattern at the top focus of the presentation for a selfie camera. Taking everything into account, the cell phone will hold a module like the Redmi Note 12 series telephones. It will in all likelihood highlight a triple back camera arrangement. The Note 12 Ace Speed Version will incorporate a 50MP fundamental camera, as indicated by the marking on the camera module.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Redmi Note 12 Pro 5G : Specs</h3>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Redmi Note 12 Pro 5G specs</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n